OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering rain clears the southeast.
OL,7,FClear spells elsewhere with wintry
OL,8,Fshowers. Later, persistent rain and
OL,9,Fhill snow reach Scotland, Northern
OL,10,FIreland and northern England. A patchy
OL,11,Ffrost will develop under the clear
OL,12,Fspells.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FSunny spells and showers,
OL,15,Fsome heavy and wintry with hail, hill
OL,16,Fsnow and isolated thunder. More
OL,17,Fprolonged showers for England and
OL,18,FWales later. Windy and blustery,
OL,19,Ffeeling colder than Friday.
